enumber\">1\u003C/span>νεν \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-transliteration\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>nen \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ΝΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-transliteration\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>NEN\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020757_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020757_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020757.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020757-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Agostiniani, in Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>According to the editor, this could be an abbreviated form of the name νενδας, which occurs in the corpus of Montagna di Marzo either in the complete form (\u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020756\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020756\u003C/a>) or in the abbreviated form (on a bowl, \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020758\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020758\u003C/a>, part of the grave goods from tomb 188 where this document was found) but is a recurrent name elsewhere in Sicily, both in Greek and indigenous contexts (Agostiniani 2018, 192). In particular, it is attested in the indigenous epigraphy on two cups from Castiglione di Ragusa (IAS II, CAS 18-19; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/9PTH7BSP\" target=\"_blank\">Agostiniani 1992\u003C/a>, p. 149 no. 8) and on the so-called Stele of Sciri (IAS II SCI 1; Agostiniani 1992, p. 148 no. 7, \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003362\" target=\"_blank\">ISic003362\u003C/a>). In the Greek documents, the name is attested in Gela (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\" target=\"_blank\">Arena 2002\u003C/a>, no. 74; \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020545\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020545\u003C/a>), in an inscription from Selinus (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/7A9T7T2J\" target=\"_blank\">Arena 1997\u003C/a>; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8SEHVAK5\" target=\"_blank\">Brugnone 2008\u003C/a>). It is also attested on a graffito from Palazzo, in Aspromonte (Lazzarini, Poccetti 2009, 125-141, in \u003Ca href=\"https://zenon.dainst.org/Record/000811858\" target=\"_blank\">Agostino, Sica 2009\u003C/a>).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Agostiniani Forthcoming MMA 64 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018 183, 185, 192, fig. 99 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[195,198,201,204,207,209,212,215,218],{"id":196,"html":197},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>νεν \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-transliteration\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>nen \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ΝΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-transliteration\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>NEN\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":199,"html":200},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020757_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020757_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020757.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020757-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":202,"html":203},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Agostiniani, in Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":205,"html":206},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{"id":205,"html":208},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{"id":210,"html":211},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>According to the editor, this could be an abbreviated form of the name νενδας, which occurs in the corpus of Montagna di Marzo either in the complete form (\u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020756\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020756\u003C/a>) or in the abbreviated form (on a bowl, \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020758\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020758\u003C/a>, part of the grave goods from tomb 188 where this document was found) but is a recurrent name elsewhere in Sicily, both in Greek and indigenous contexts (Agostiniani 2018, 192). In particular, it is attested in the indigenous epigraphy on two cups from Castiglione di Ragusa (IAS II, CAS 18-19; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/9PTH7BSP\" target=\"_blank\">Agostiniani 1992\u003C/a>, p. 149 no. 8) and on the so-called Stele of Sciri (IAS II SCI 1; Agostiniani 1992, p. 148 no. 7, \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003362\" target=\"_blank\">ISic003362\u003C/a>). In the Greek documents, the name is attested in Gela (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\" target=\"_blank\">Arena 2002\u003C/a>, no. 74; \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020545\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020545\u003C/a>), in an inscription from Selinus (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/7A9T7T2J\" target=\"_blank\">Arena 1997\u003C/a>; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8SEHVAK5\" target=\"_blank\">Brugnone 2008\u003C/a>). It is also attested on a graffito from Palazzo, in Aspromonte (Lazzarini, Poccetti 2009, 125-141, in \u003Ca href=\"https://zenon.dainst.org/Record/000811858\" target=\"_blank\">Agostino, Sica 2009\u003C/a>).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":213,"html":214},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Agostiniani Forthcoming MMA 64 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018 183, 185, 192, fig. 99 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscripti